Class TestBase

    public class TestBase
extends java.nio.file.SimpleFileVisitor<java.nio.file.Path>
    This is a base class for setting up a test environment. Using properties files, it contains the necessary information for 1. defining and providing attributes 2. defining and instantiating the PDP engine 3. creating PEP requests and calling the PDP engine
    Author:
    pameladragosh
